examples.en: He struck me on the chin.
He struck his hand on the table.
Two ships struck in the channel.
The band struck up a tango.
The bullet struck him in the leg.
The tree was struck by lightning.
She struck him hard across the face.
He struck me by his knowledge.
He struck his knee with his hand.
He was struck dead by a thunderbolt.
I have struck out my own line.
The cyclist was struck by a car.
I struck sharply upon the glass.
He struck me aside with his fist.
